HEADWORD: Kinky
<hw>Kink"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Full of
kinks; liable to kink or curl; <as>as, <ex>kinky</ex>
hair</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Queer; eccentric; unconventional; crotchety.</def>
<mark>[Colloq. U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kinnikinic</ent>⟦br⟧
